# POS / Presentation

## API `/api/pos/*` (Sanctum, `UserModel`)

Контроллер: `app/Http/Controllers/Pos/PosController.php`  
Ответ заказа после mutation: trait `RendersPosOrder` → `PosOrderReadModelBuilder`.

| Метод | Путь | Handler / Query |
|-------|------|-----------------|
| POST | `login` | — (`UserModel` + token) |
| GET | `dashboard` | `GetPosDashboardQueryHandler` → `{ counts, avg_work_duration_seconds }` |
| GET | `orders/counts` | `GetPosOrderCountsQueryHandler` |
| GET | `orders?status=&page=` | `GetPosOrdersQueryHandler` → `PosOrderPresenter::list` |
| GET | `orders/{id}` | `GetPosOrderDetailQueryHandler` → `PosOrderReadModelBuilder` |
| POST | `orders/{id}/take-to-work` | `TakeOrderToWorkHandler` |
| POST | `orders/{id}/waiting-parts` | `MarkOrderWaitingForPartsHandler` |
| POST | `orders/{id}/resume` | `ResumeOrderHandler` |
| POST | `orders/{id}/works` | `AddWorkHandler` |
| DELETE | `orders/{id}/works` | `RemoveWorkHandler` (body: `sort_order`) |
| PATCH | `orders/{id}/internal-notes` | `UpdateInternalNotesHandler` |
| POST | `orders/{id}/mark-ready` | `MarkOrderReadyHandler` |
| POST | `orders/{id}/return-to-work` | `ReturnOrderToWorkHandler` |
| GET | `warehouse/items?query=&page=` | `SearchWarehouseItemsQueryHandler` |
| GET | `equipment?query=&page=` | `SearchEquipmentQueryHandler` |
| GET | `equipment/{id}/orders` | `GetEquipmentOrderHistoryQueryHandler` |

**Фильтрация:** списки, счётчики, dashboard, detail, mutations — `master_id = auth()->id()` (кроме `equipment/{id}/orders`).

**List vs detail:** список — `PosOrderPresenter` без enrichment; карточка — `PosOrderReadModelBuilder` (+ equipment, master, имена материалов).

## Auth

```
POST /api/pos/login → { token, master: { id, name, email } }
```

- Middleware: `auth:sanctum` на всех маршрутах кроме `login`
- Guard `web` — Filament; POS — тот же `UserModel` через Sanctum token
- Server logout / revoke token — **нет**; только клиентский `posStore.logout()`

## Vue SPA `/pos`

Layout: `pages/PosPage.vue` (gate: login → Sidebar + Header + `<router-view>`).  
`App.vue` не рендерит `MainLayout` для `/pos*`.

### Router (`resources/js/router/index.js`)

| Path | Name | Page |
|------|------|------|
| `/pos/dashboard` | `pos.dashboard` | `DashboardPage` |
| `/pos/orders/new` | `pos.orders.new` | `OrdersNewPage` |
| `/pos/orders/active` | `pos.orders.active` | `OrdersActivePage` |
| `/pos/orders/waiting-parts` | `pos.orders.waiting-parts` | `OrdersWaitingPartsPage` |
| `/pos/orders/in-work/:id` | `pos.orders.in-work` | `OrderInWorkPage` |
| `/pos/orders/completed` | `pos.orders.completed` | `OrdersCompletedPage` |
| `/pos/warehouse` | `pos.warehouse.index` | `WarehousePage` |
| `/pos/equipment/search` | `pos.equipment.search` | `EquipmentSearchPage` |

Router guards **нет** — проверка сессии в `PosPage.vue`.

**Без маршрута (мертвый код):** `WarehousePartsPage`, `WarehouseMaterialsPage`.

### Store / Services

| Модуль | Роль |
|--------|------|
| `stores/posStore.js` | login, restoreSession, counts, logout; `localStorage`: `pos_token`, `pos_user` |
| `services/pos/OrderService.js` | все `/api/pos/orders/*` |
| `services/pos/WarehouseService.js` | warehouse items |
| `services/pos/EquipmentService.js` | equipment search + history |

### Components

`LoginForm`, `Sidebar`, `Header`, `OrderStats`, `OrderCard`, `OrderDetailsModal`

### Composables

`usePosOrderDisplay`, `useAutoRefresh` (списки 20–30 с), `useHeaderNavigation`

### Axios (`bootstrap.js`)

`/api/pos/*` (кроме `/login`) → `Authorization: Bearer {pos_token}` из `localStorage`.

Моков API нет — POS всегда ходит на бэкенд.

`AssignMasterToOrder`, `LinkEquipmentToOrder`, `SetWorkPrices`, `RecalculateOrderPrice`, `AddMaterialToOrder`, `RemoveMaterialFromOrder`, `IssueOrder`, `CancelOrder`, PDF — `OrderManageActions` в `/cp`.
